column5: If you qualify for Senior Discounts, this is the code for you.  ATD: At The Doctor's BTW: Bring The Wheelchair BYOT: Bring Your Own Teeth CBM: Covered By Medicare CUATSC: See You At The Senior Center FWB: Friend With Beta Blockers FWIW: Forgot Where I Was FYI: Found Your Insulin? GGPBL: Gotta Go, Pacemaker Battery Low! GHA: Got Heartburn Again HGBM: Had Good Bowel Movement IMHO: Is My Hearing-Aid On? LMDO: Laughing My Dentures Out LWO: Lawrence Welk's On OMMR: On My Massage Recliner OMSG: Oh My! Sorry, Gas. ROFL... CGU: Rolling On The Floor Laughing... And Can't Get Up SGGP: Sorry, Gotta Go Pee TTYL: Talk To You Louder WAITT: Who Am I Talking To? WTFA: Wet The Furniture Again WTP: Where's The Prunes? WWNO: Walker Wheels Need Oil
MQFYBB:    Mod que for you Billy Bob ....   eh Roy?  how dare he make fun...

My step dad managed to dig himself into a hole because he added "lol" to the end of every text he sent to my mom (thinking it meant "lots of love" as she told him about how her knee had been really bothering her (and dislocated the odd time)
